Package de.rwth.swc.coffee4j.junit

Class CombinatorialTestMethodContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth.swc.coffee4j.junit.CombinatorialTestMethodContext
  • class CombinatorialTestMethodContext
extends java.lang.Object
    One context for a complete CombinatorialTest. Handles concrete parameter resolving using ArgumentsAggregator and ArgumentConverter.

    This is more or less a copy of ParameterizedTestMethodContext from the junit-jupiter-params project.
